data.description: Take a look at your new home. Beautifully maintaned 5 bedroom home on a rare corner lot. MINUTES from downtown, schools,shopping and resturaunts. Tile and laminite flooring and extra closet shelving throughout .Double Pantry as well as a seperate walk in kitchen closet. Double sinks in both bathrooms and a roomy half bath-powder room conveniently placed for the whole first floor. The backyard coverd deck covers stamped concrete patio and surrounded by a solid wood fence. The spacious den with wood burning fireplace overlooks the eat in kitchen and patio.Four bedrooms upstairs share a bath and reading knook.
